Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.86,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看電視的時候，請保持房間明亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.83,0:00:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐遠一點再看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.69,0:00:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好無聊喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.97,0:00:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.31,0:00:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家也想去的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.81,0:00:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要跟來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.45,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳來學校只會添麻煩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.55,0:01:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳來學校只會添麻煩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.19,0:01:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.22,0:01:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的話就可以去學校了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.50,0:01:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能在一起就覺得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.50,0:01:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使被罵了也還是\N好喜歡好喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.34,0:01:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算一副臭臉\N也依然是那麼迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.41,0:01:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請實現我的願望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.25,0:01:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧 一起來吧\N一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.45,0:01:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧\N一起來吧 一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.45,0:01:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來 一起來\N一起來 一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.69,0:01:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一．起．來．吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.49,0:01:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那天以來的悸動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.03,0:01:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論何時都希望能感覺的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.37,0:01:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡都只想和你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.44,0:01:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什麼都好讓人心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷入戀愛的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都好像魔法師一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.99,0:02:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是微不足道的小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.96,0:02:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以讓人高興起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.53,0:02:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能在一起就覺得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.26,0:02:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使被罵了也還是\N好喜歡好喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.40,0:02:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算一副臭臉\N也依然是那麼迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.44,0:02:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請實現我的願望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.41,0:02:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧 一起來吧\N一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.34,0:02:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧\N一起來吧 一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.41,0:02:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來 一起來 一起來\N一起來 一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.99,0:02:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大膽!被抱了好高興喔!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.37,0:02:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕地...輕輕地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.07,0:02:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~就差一點點了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.61,0:03:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒，開門的時要輕一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦，看的出來是我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.99,0:03:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那，再來要玩什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.71,0:03:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒\N乾爹A不是剛剛才說過了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.75,0:03:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦，這樣還看得出是我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.45,0:03:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼~?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.95,0:03:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒該不會是想讓我們嚇一跳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都有那個意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是友紀不在，覺得很寂寞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再來的話，不管是什麼打扮\N我們都裝作很吃驚的樣子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.67,0:04:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看莉采兒高興的表情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了 準備好了嗎?\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你、你是什麼人啊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.48,0:04:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的傢伙，難道是哪裡派來\N想搶走可愛的莉采兒的間諜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，看你那臉就知道一定是這樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.65,0:04:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃...別把剛洗的衣服給弄髒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,積了很多好不容易才洗完的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.19,0:04:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都是莉采兒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是莉采兒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.36,0:04:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.86,0:04:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒，這太明顯了啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鏘~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.70,0:04:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇~沒有人發現耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.87,0:04:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉、莉采兒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真、真是嚇了我們一跳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.94,0:04:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會是莉采兒呢...對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.44,0:04:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.31,0:04:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全沒有發現呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.15,0:04:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是、是啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.38,0:04:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，這樣就沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那，我出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，慢走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.76,0:04:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要小心車子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.76,0:05:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說要出去\N那副打扮是要到哪兒去啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一提...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.34,0:05:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一提...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.27,0:05:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我老公買來\N要在宴會上戴的鼻眼鏡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.54,0:05:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事無所謂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.78,0:05:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了到了\N可是我現在並不是莉采兒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.99,0:05:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了，小汪汪\N我是莉采兒這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.99,0:05:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要對老公保密喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.20,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇~學校是這麼大的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.00,0:05:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣要找老公可辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.51,0:05:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去嘍，喔~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.01,0:05:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為如此\N這裡會變成這樣再變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.31,0:05:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所求得的答案就變成這樣，不過...\N大家都懂了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.45,0:06:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公~ 老公~\N你在哪裡啊~ 老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.16,0:06:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃...啊...嗯...\N那時候，就光源氏的心境來說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.96,0:06:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點出來呀\N老公啊~ 老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.33,0:06:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最帥氣的老公啊~ 老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.61,0:06:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀你是在哪裡啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.24,0:06:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最愛的老老老老老公啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡一個人也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.27,0:06:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就叫好戲在後頭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's Go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會講的地方考試會考出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.77,0:06:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要東張西望的，給我好好聽課!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.88,0:07:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼\N我非得學這些早就知道的東西不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是無聊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.59,0:07:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不在這裡\N老公你到底在哪裡嘛...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走路時不看好前面還真不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.30,0:07:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?眼鏡眼鏡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，有了有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太可愛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.05,0:07:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那名可愛的少女是誰啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變裝變裝...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那...那個是...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.19,0:07:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小、小、小熊...內、內...\N我說不出口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!我身為一個紳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.00,0:07:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎能偷窺少女的內...\N那白色的東西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.50,0:07:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，真是位可愛的少女啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.91,0:08:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一次有好好看前面了說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.14,0:08:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個\N要快點找到老公才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.52,0:08:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，三年B班的同學們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.85,0:08:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到教室以前都還是校外教學呢\N隊伍不要亂掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.72,0:08:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.53,0:08:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會斷了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，岩城同學?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?沒什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛你盯著老師在發呆吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真不死心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.51,0:08:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.78,0:08:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校已經找10遍了\N可是到處都找不到老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.15,0:08:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒力氣找了啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.79,0:08:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.06,0:08:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到一個好辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.57,0:09:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去，大家都已經先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一群無情的傢伙...嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.54,0:09:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面的情形似乎有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.05,0:09:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我進去看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.68,0:09:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岩城同學!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.35,0:09:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要~!救救我，老公~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.33,0:09:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我啊，老公~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在搞什麼啊，莉采兒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.33,0:09:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.70,0:09:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對!你是誰啊\N我又不是莉采兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快踩煞車，煞車啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你踩煞車了嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是煞車啊~?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連煞車都不知道就不要騎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.22,0:09:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停下來!停下來!\N可是停不下來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.02,0:09:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停不下來也沒關係\N就別再跑了啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那傢伙會來學校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.23,0:10:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要撞上了，不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快不行了啦~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.87,0:10:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣來不及的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.54,0:10:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.55,0:10:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，要撞上了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.76,0:10:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.90,0:10:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公...是你救了我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.28,0:10:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是第一次被老公救耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.91,0:10:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不好笑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.91,0:10:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊\N騎著車跑來跑去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.15,0:10:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家想說騎那個的話\N就可以快一點找到老公了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰要妳來找我啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.29,0:11:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要自作主張，妳這白痴!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.33,0:11:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家費了不少苦心的說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂、別哭啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.93,0:11:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等、等一下\N想在這裡搞爆炸啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，要哭了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.57,0:11:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，我知道了啦\N總之別哭啊，莉采兒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撐不住了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.11,0:11:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~真是的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個應該是B班的岩城同學吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.08,0:11:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟那個少女是什麼關係啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭，還不能哭啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不能放炸彈啊!\N不要哭，莉采兒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，這裡好像沒什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點小爆炸應該沒什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥! 公、公車站!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不行啊~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不能讓它爆炸啊，莉采兒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.64,0:11:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.97,0:11:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，大家往這邊唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不行啊~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.61,0:11:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帳~怎麼到哪\N都有人冒出來啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.61,0:12:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公從剛才就一直抱著我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.12,0:12:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這妻子是多麼的幸福啊\N老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.99,0:12:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊了\N我已經不會想哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.52,0:12:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.36,0:12:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得被我最喜歡的老公抱著\N怎麼可以哭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.36,0:12:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊，都回到家啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘖，真沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.04,0:12:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回學校去了，別再跑來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.54,0:12:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶~不抱了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.74,0:12:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是我自己想抱的\N白痴!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.01,0:12:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家還想要抱抱的說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱嘛~ 抱嘛~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.76,0:12:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊\N衝啊 衝啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.30,0:12:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊 衝啊\N衝啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.77,0:12:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊 衝啊 衝啊\N老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.04,0:13:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你了 衝啊衝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.32,0:13:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人和女人真是難以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.79,0:13:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了查清楚我去了圖書館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.42,0:13:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對比他年幼的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.46,0:13:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公是一點興趣也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.80,0:13:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是人家好喜歡他\N所以我不會哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.57,0:13:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不氣餒，不逃避\N更不會失去勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.71,0:13:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信總有一天春天會到來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.72,0:13:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿出認真的力量\N認真的力量向前衝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.33,0:13:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊\N衝啊 衝啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.60,0:13:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊 衝啊\N衝啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.10,0:14:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊 衝啊 衝啊\N老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.50,0:14:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你了 衝啊衝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.84,0:14:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃，那個\N我叫岩城建司，是友紀的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是他媽媽真理子\N是個家庭主婦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.12,0:14:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從莉采兒來了之後\N家裡變的很熱鬧，每天都很愉快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.99,0:14:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是兒子好，跟你就是不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.79,0:14:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(次回 成功! 我們一起去了!?)\N什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.19,0:14:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃，那個\N我叫岩城建司，是友紀的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.80,0:14:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個上班族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.87,0:14:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是他媽媽真理子\N是個家庭主婦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.37,0:14:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從莉采兒來了之後\N家裡變的很熱鬧，每天都很愉快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.51,0:14:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能多個可愛的女兒是很高興啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是房子再這樣被破壞下去的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.94,0:14:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛\N反正會幫我們修好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.14,0:14:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這、這麼一說也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.38,0:14:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用國家預算改建耶\N不是很幸運嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.22,0:14:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是、是這樣嗎?\N哈哈哈...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.88,0:14:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是兒子好\N跟你就是不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.65,0:14:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(次回 成功! 我們一起去了!?)\N什麼?
